(2, 36, '5 Night 6 Days Thailand Trip', 'International Trip', 25000, 'Welcome toThailand Trip', '', 'Embark on an unforgettable journey through our Thailand tour package with a captivating 5-day Thailand itinerary, where adventure, relaxation, and cultural discovery await at every turn. Your adventure begins in Phuket, Thailand\'s largest island, where a dynamic blend of culture, nightlife, and natural beauty awaits. Settle into your accommodation and prepare to immerse yourself in the wonders of this enchanting destination. The next day, embark on a thrilling Phi Phi Island tour, where you\'ll explore the breathtaking beauty of these iconic islands by a speedboat. Let our experienced guides lead you to marvel at the wonders of Maya Bay, Viking Cave, and Monkey Beach, surrounded by stunning limestone cliffs and crystal-clear waters teeming with vibrant marine life. <br><br>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe excitement continues with a full-day James Bond Island tour, where you\'ll board a speedboat and journey to Khao Ping Khan, famously known as James Bond Island. As you cruise through Phang Nga Bay, marvel at the dramatic scenery and explore enchanting mangrove forests. Enjoy kayaking around Hong Island before indulging in a delicious lunch on Panyee Island. Relax on the serene shores of Naka Noi Island, soaking in the beauty of your surroundings. As your adventure in Phuket unfolds, take a step back in time with a Phuket City Tour, where you\'ll explore the island\'s rich cultural heritage. ', '1741080394.png', '1741080394.1png', '1741080394.2png', 'Thailand', '1741080394.3jpg', 'Phuket International Airport to Phuket International Airport', 'Packages', '6 Days', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2, 37, '8 Night 9 Days Thailand Tour ', 'Internatiional Trip', 400000, 'Welcome to Thailand  Trip', '', 'Commence on a magnificent Thai journey that seamlessly combines the unique charms of Pattaya, the dynamic energy of Bangkok, the tropical paradise of Phuket, and the natural beauty of Krabi. Get ready for an adventure of a lifetime! \r\nPattaya provides the ideal blend of relaxation and excitement. From there, your adventure continues to the bustling heart of Thailand, Bangkok. This metropolis harmoniously combines ancient traditions with modern marvels. Explore iconic temples like Wat Pho and Wat Arun, cruise along the Chao Phraya River, and savor the vibrant markets and delicious street food. Bangkok\'s nightlife is legendary, featuring rooftop bars, night markets, and cultural performances that will captivate you. Your next destination is the tropical island paradise of Phuket. <br><br>\r\nSurrounded by crystal-clear waters, Phuket boasts world-class beaches such as Patong, Kata, and Karon. Enjoy sun-filled days, water adventures, snorkeling, and diving to explore the rich underwater world. Discover the island\'s cultural heritage in Old Phuket Town and savor exquisite Thai cuisine. Whether you\'re seeking relaxation or adventure, Phuket offers it all. Conclude your Thai adventure in the natural beauty of Krabi. ', '1741080980.png', '17410863121457.png', '1741080980.2png', 'Thailand', '1741080980.3png', 'Phuket International Airport to Phuket International Airport', 'Packages', '9 Days', '', '', '', '', ''),
(5, 38, '6 Night 7 Days Russia Tour Package', 'International Trip', 145000, 'Welcome to Russia Trip', '', 'mbark on an unforgettable journey through Russia, a country rich in history, culture, and breathtaking landscapes. From the majestic architecture of Moscow’s Red Square to the artistic treasures of St. Petersburg, Russia offers a perfect blend of tradition and modernity.\r\nExplore iconic landmarks like the Kremlin, St. Basil’s Cathedral, and the Hermitage Museum. Cruise along the scenic rivers, experience the famous Trans-Siberian Railway, and immerse yourself in the local charm of quaint villages and vibrant cities.<br><br>\r\nWhether you want to witness the Northern Lights in Murmansk, ski in the Caucasus Mountains, or relax by the serene Lake Baikal, Russia has something for every traveler.', '17410860025666.png', '1741081745.1png', '17410860703236.png', 'Russia', '1741081745.3png', 'Airport to  Airport', 'Packages', '7 Days', '', '', '', '', ''),
(9, 39, '7 Night 8 Days Egypt Tour Packages', 'International Trip', 60000, 'Welcome to Egypt Trip', '', 'Embark on the Pharaohs Nile Cruise Adventure — a journey through the heart of ancient Egypt, where history and luxury blend seamlessly. As you sail down the majestic Nile River, you’ll witness breathtaking landscapes, timeless monuments, and the vibrant culture of Egypt.\r\n\r\nYour adventure begins in Cairo, the bustling capital, where you’ll explore the Great Pyramids of Giza and the enigmatic Sphinx. After soaking in the grandeur of these world wonders, you’ll board a luxurious cruise ship, your home for the next few days.<br><br>\r\nGlide along the lifeline of Egypt, stopping at iconic destinations like Luxor and Aswan. In Luxor, marvel at the Karnak Temple and the Valley of the Kings, where ancient pharaohs rest in elaborately decorated tombs. In Aswan, visit the picturesque Philae Temple and take a serene felucca ride on the Nile.\r\n\r\nThroughout the cruise, you’ll enjoy world-class amenities, including comfortable cabins with stunning river views, gourmet dining, and entertainment inspired by Egyptian traditions. Engage in cultural activities, relax on the sun deck, or unwind with a spa treatment.\r\n\r\nAs the sun sets over the Nile, you’ll experience the magic of Egypt’s golden sands and historic marvels, creating memories that last a lifetime. The Pharaohs Nile Cruise Adventure is not just a trip — it’s a voyage through time, where every moment tells a story of splendor and mystery.', '1741082543.png', '1741082543.1png', '1741082543.2jpg', 'Egypt', '1741082543.3png', 'Airport to  Airport', 'Packages', '8 Days', '', '', '', '', ''),
(11, 40, '5 Night 6 Days Paris Trip Package', 'International Trip', 95629, 'Welcome to Paris  Trip', '', 'Explore the magic of Paris with our exclusive package priced at just ₹95,626 per package. This specially curated trip offers a perfect blend of elegance, romance, and adventure in the City of Lights. Enjoy a luxurious 5-night, 6-day stay in the heart of Paris with daily breakfast and dinner included. Discover iconic landmarks like the Eiffel Tower, Louvre Museum, Notre-Dame Cathedral, and the Champs-Élysées through guided tours.<br><br> Experience a mesmerizing evening cruise along the scenic Seine River and take advantage of comfortable airport transfers and local transport. With ample time for shopping and leisure at chic boutiques and vibrant streets, this package ensures an authentic and unforgettable Parisian experience. In addition to these incredible highlights, you’ll also get the opportunity to indulge in Paris’s world-renowned cuisine, explore charming neighborhoods like Montmartre and Le Marais, and capture picture-perfect moments at Trocadéro Gardens. Whether you’re strolling along the romantic Seine, marveling at the city’s architectural wonders, or enjoying a coffee at a quaint sidewalk café, every moment in Paris promises to be extraordinary. Book your Paris adventure today and create memories that will last a lifetime!\r\n\r\n', '1741083069.png', '1741083069.1png', '1741083069.2png', 'Paris', '1741083069.3png', 'Airport to  Airport', 'Packages', '6 Days', '', '', '', '', ''),
(10, 41, '5 Night 6 Days Malaysia Tour Package', 'International Trip', 80000, 'Welcome to Malaysia  Trip', '', 'Embark on an unforgettable journey to Malaysia — a destination where adventure, culture, and relaxation come together in perfect harmony. Our carefully curated travel packages offer the best of this Southeast Asian paradise, whether you’re drawn to bustling cities, serene beaches, or breathtaking natural landscapes.\r\n\r\nExplore Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia’s vibrant capital, where iconic landmarks like the Petronas Twin Towers meet lively street markets and mouthwatering local cuisine. Experience the awe of the Batu Caves and enjoy world-class shopping in modern malls and traditional bazaars.\r\n\r\nFor beach lovers, Langkawi awaits with its crystal-clear waters and luxurious resorts. Dive into thrilling water sports, ride the famous cable car for panoramic views, or unwind on pristine sandy beaches. Penang, the \'Pearl of the Orient,\' offers colonial charm, stunning street art, and some of the world’s best street food.<br><br>\r\n\r\nNature enthusiasts will love the lush Cameron Highlands, perfect for exploring tea plantations and scenic hiking trails. If you crave a wilder adventure, head to Borneo’s rainforests to encounter orangutans and exotic wildlife in their natural habitat.', '1741083738.png', '1741083738.1jpg', '1741083738.2png', 'Malaysia', '1741083738.3png', 'Airport to  Airport', 'Packages', '6 Days', '', '', '', '', '');

